{"tid":657296,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《福爾摩斯3》2020聖誕上映 對撼《阿凡達2》","createTime":"2018-05-08T03:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T15:43:10.000Z","uid":41343,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"698b715c1255fae0af2a2059bf35bdb1b936bb6f","tid":657296,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:39:26.000Z","msg":"根據美國媒體 Deadline Hollywood 的報導，由小勞勃&middot;道尼（Robert Downey Jr.）與裘&middot;德洛（Jude Law）主演的電影《福爾摩斯 Sherlock Holmes》系列電影第三部《福爾摩斯3 Sherlock Holmes 3》，即將於 2020 年聖誕檔期在美國上映，除了兩位主角確定回歸外，報導也指出本集的劇本將由克里斯&middot;布蘭卡托（Chris Brancato）執筆，第二集《福爾摩斯2：詭影遊戲 Sherlock Holmes: A Game of Shadows》喬&middot;西佛（Joel Silver）、蘇珊&middot;道尼（Susan Downey）與萊昂納爾&middot;威格蘭（Lionel Wigram）則再次擔任監製，至於前兩部電影的導演蓋&middot;瑞奇（Guy Ritchie）則尚未確定是否回歸擔任導演一職。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據報導指出，目前確定回歸《福爾摩斯3 Sherlock Holmes 3》的演員還包含飾演艾琳&middot;愛德勒的瑞秋&middot;麥亞當斯（Rachel McAdams），不過 Deadline Hollywood 也表示，本片的檔期將於同樣在 2020 年 12 月 18 日上映的強片《阿凡達2 Avatar 2》檔期強碰，巧妙的是在 2009 年首部《福爾摩斯 Sherlock Holmes》也與《阿凡達 Avatar》檔期相近，小勞勃&middot;道尼與裘&middot;德洛能否展現魅力迎戰傳奇導演詹姆士&middot;卡麥隆的神作《阿凡達2 Avatar 2》也是媒體關注的焦點。"},{"pid":"e3be9983d1bbb0d0eb2278224819650c63ebb276","tid":657296,"uid":32979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:40:10.000Z","msg":"兩班波喎"},{"pid":"61052f3575231f671554ff9cac7223d1ef2abc57","tid":657296,"uid":50060,"like":27,"dislike":90,"score":-63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:42:16.000Z","msg":"投下票, 大家覺得<br />\nIronman 演得好既 請正評<br />\nDr. Strange 演得好既 請負評"},{"pid":"85fcd2838b01b8b56436e0159ef73e9919a78b84","tid":657296,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:44:13.000Z","msg":"有生之年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eba0a74e5c7499318385af3391b124c369048a70","tid":657296,"uid":36167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep